title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 8 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H3 – Aug 8 2022
description:
Georgia Senate candidate Herschel Walker joins Clay and Buck to make his case against Raphael Warnock. Gordon Ramsay outrages the internet choosing a lamb to cook. CNN's Brian Stelter admits Hunter Biden's laptop is real two years later. NYT admits covid school closings were a mistake. Health experts who locked down country for covid won't advise gay men to refrain from orgies to avoid monkeypox. Caller on eating animals he raised.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
